# Supabase Database Schema Documentation

## Table Definitions

### Authentication & Users

**users** - Supabase Auth users table (extends `auth.users`)
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|--------------|-------------|
| id | uuid | PK | User ID from Supabase Auth |
| email | string | UK, NOT NULL | User email address |
| created_at | timestamp | NOT NULL | Account creation timestamp |

**user_profiles** - Extended user profile data
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|--------------|-------------|
| id | uuid | PK | Auto-generated profile ID |
| user_id | uuid | FK → users.id, UK | Reference to auth user |
| full_name | string | | User's display name |
| avatar_url | string | | Profile image URL |
| updated_at | timestamp | | Last profile update |

---

### Core Entities

**cities** - Analyzed city/location records
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|--------------|-------------|
| id | uuid | PK | Auto-generated city ID |
| name | string | NOT NULL | City name |
| state | string | NOT NULL | State/region |
| country | string | NOT NULL | Country |
| created_at | timestamp | NOT NULL | Creation timestamp |
| owner_id | uuid | FK → users.id | City owner |

---

### Political Entities

**political_figures** - Politicians associated with cities
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|--------------|-------------|
| id | uuid | PK | Auto-generated ID |
| city_id | uuid | FK → cities.id | Associated city |
| name | string | NOT NULL | Politician name |
| position | string | NOT NULL | Office/position held |
| party | string | | Political party |
| jurisdiction | string | | Governing jurisdiction |
| source_url | string | | Reference URL |

**political_commentary** - Quotes/statements from politicians
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|--------------|-------------|
| id | uuid | PK | Auto-generated ID |
| political_figure_id | uuid | FK → political_figures.id | Source politician |
| city_id | uuid | FK → cities.id | Related city |
| source_url | string | | Article/source link |
| comment | text | NOT NULL | Quoted statement |
| reliability_score | float | | 0-1 reliability rating |
| created_at | timestamp | NOT NULL | Record creation |

**social_media_posts** - Social media activity
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|--------------|-------------|
| id | uuid | PK | Auto-generated ID |
| political_figure_id | uuid | FK → political_figures.id | Author |
| platform | string | NOT NULL | e.g., Twitter, Facebook |
| tweet_id | string | | Platform post ID |
| text | text | NOT NULL | Post content |
| created_at | timestamp | | Post timestamp |
| engagement | jsonb | | Likes, retweets, etc. |

---

### Legislation

**legislation** - Local laws/ordinances
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|--------------|-------------|
| id | uuid | PK | Auto-generated ID |
| city_id | uuid | FK → cities.id | Related city |
| title | string | NOT NULL | Bill/ordinance title |
| summary | text | | Brief summary |
| body | text | | Full text/content |
| created_at | timestamp | NOT NULL | Record creation |
| updated_at | timestamp | | Last update |

**legislation_sources** - Reference sources for legislation
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|--------------|-------------|
| id | uuid | PK | Auto-generated ID |
| legislation_id | uuid | FK → legislation.id | Related legislation |
| url | string | NOT NULL | Source URL |
| organization | string | | Publishing org |
| reliability_score | float | | Source reliability |

---

### Reports & Tasks

**reports** - Generated analysis reports
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|--------------|-------------|
| id | uuid | PK | Auto-generated ID |
| city_id | uuid | FK → cities.id | Related city |
| title | string | NOT NULL | Report title |
| markdown_report | text | NOT NULL | Full markdown content |
| summary | text | | Brief summary |
| created_at | timestamp | NOT NULL | Creation timestamp |
| updated_at | timestamp | | Last update |

**tasks** - Background job tracking
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|--------------|-------------|
| id | uuid | PK | Auto-generated ID |
| city_id | uuid | FK → cities.id | Related city |
| user_id | uuid | FK → users.id | Requesting user |
| status | string | NOT NULL | pending/processing/completed/failed |
| result | text | | Task output result |
| error | text | | Error message if failed |
| created_at | timestamp | NOT NULL | Creation timestamp |
| updated_at | timestamp | | Last status update |

---

## Index Recommendations

```sql
-- Performance indexes
CREATE INDEX idx_political_figures_city ON political_figures(city_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_legislation_city ON legislation(city_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_reports_city ON reports(city_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_tasks_user ON tasks(user_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_tasks_status ON tasks(status);
CREATE INDEX idx_political_commentary_figure ON political_commentary(political_figure_id);
```

## RLS Policies (Row Level Security)

All tables should enable RLS and create policies:
- Users can only read/write their own data
- Public read for cities, legislation, political_figures (read-only)
- Reports can be public or private based on user preference